## ProjectÂ Overview

This repository hosts a **reproducible data pipeline** (PythonÂ +Â SQLite) and **Powerâ€¯BI visuals** that answer six core marketing questions about customers, products, and revenue trends. All charts and tables are built directly from the source CSVsâ€”no manual Excel wrangling required.

