## BusinessÂ Questions

The project answers (and visualises) these questions:

| # | Question                                                 | Technique                             |
| - | -------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| 1 | What are our customer segments and how do they behave?   | RFMÂ + Kâ€‘means                         |
| 2 | Which products generate the most revenue and margin?     | Pareto & cohort analyses              |
| 3 | How does revenue trend by country over time?             | Timeâ€‘series decomposition             |
| 4 | What is the daily revenue forecast for the next 90Â days? | ProphetÂ forecast & uncertainty ribbon |
| 5 | Which marketing campaign drives the highest AOV?         | SQLÂ + DAXÂ comparison                  |
| 6 | What KPIs should leadership track weekly?                | Live dashboard tiles                  |

