> **How to add it:**
>
> 1. Open **sales\_dashboard.pbix** in **Powerâ€¯BI Desktop** and navigate to the *Overview* page.
> 2. Click **FileÂ â†’Â ExportÂ â†’Â Export toÂ PNG** (or press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Shift</kbd>+<kbd>S</kbd>).
